    <JadeMethod name="doClearNoteRecords" id="e18a24b7-741a-4df6-ac9a-820464782b52">
        <source>doClearNoteRecords(_doClearOthers: Boolean; _doClearCurrentView : Boolean);
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
23/06/2025	navkc1 JIRA MTN 34973 MTN | Pagination - Work Order Enquiry

