30/05/2021  navma1  ChangeRequest 51002: MTN - Web Portal Cargo Work Orders
16/08/2022  navma1	Bug 54403: MTN - Work Order Maintenance - No Voyage Task Types is Shown on Lookup Screen
26/11/2024	navkc1 JIRA Story MTN-19092: EUP | 54014 - Work Orders Enhancements - Improved Search and usability
*/
vars
	sht				: CMUI_Sheet;
begin
	
